1. *Kopile* su uživale u kupanju u bazenu. (The puppies enjoyed swimming in the pool.)

2. *Kopilama* se daju prehrambeni obroci uveče. (The puppies are given meals in the evening.)

3. *Kopilu* je pronašao slučajni prolaznik. (A passerby found the puppy.)

4. *Kopilom* se brinuo njegov vlasnik. (His owner took care of the puppy.)

5. *Kopili* su se igrali na travi. (The puppies were playing in the grass.)